{"tid":263508,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術角度]如果變番一角一制樓價係咪會跌?","createTime":"2017-05-30T05:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T05:40:00.000Z","uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db030dcdf2cf4f5705a91a1fa13ba5bbb6a48795","tid":263508,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"如今香港樓價已經升到一個痴左線既地步<br />\n<br />\n但依然仲好多人入市去買買買炒炒炒<br />\n<br />\n原因相信都係因為對香港而家呢套制度,法治等等信得過<br />\n<br />\n如果假設聽日就廢一國兩制廢特區地位，變成廣東省一個市仔<br />\n<br />\n設黨委書記，廢ICAC用中紀委取而代之。<br />\n<br />\n法律更加唔洗講，基本法唔再用，全面實行大陸法律。<br />\n<br />\n港元更加即時取消，即時用人仔作為香港市既貨幣，好似大陸其他地方咁。<br />\n<br />\n咁到時，香港冇晒自己果套之後，啲投資者仲會唔會買香港樓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我諗近香港既後生仔如果想上車，應該積極推動廢除一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n所有野都有代價，如果比番大陸管可以換來有樓住，勉強都係公平交易既。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9639e2a954480be448da60568f5cbb21b21c1f","tid":263508,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:35:48.000Z","msg":"TOPIC 將國打左做角<br />\n<br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb63e886965fe64966834ded9ad123b418d00ba","tid":263508,"uid":3740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:39:10.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 紅色的白色 )<br />\n<br />\n腦都唔撚用 低質會員 block 得"},{"pid":"eb14fdb3eaaabf9f008dd1fc300b08a2c3f9550b","tid":263508,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>( Show Blocked User - 紅色的白色 )<br />\n<br />\n腦都唔撚用 低質會員 block 得</blockquote><br />\n<br /